        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"speech balloon\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f4ac\" role=\"img\" title=\"speech balloon\">:speech_balloon:</span> alexcrichton created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13472#discussion_r3294859211\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>It's ok to skip the test on this one, we don't really have a great way of testing internal assertions and <code>bail_bug!</code>, and that's just something we'll have to live with over time. I'd prefer to avoid testing internal details like this as an alternative.</p>\n</blockquote>",
